spec_data.Name: golang-github-PuerkitoBio-purell-unit-test-devel
spec_data.Description:
Purell is a tiny Go library to normalize URLs. It returns a pure URL.
Based on the wikipedia paper (URL_normalization) and the RFC 3986 document.

This package contains unit tests for project
providing packages with github.com/PuerkitoBio/purell prefix.
